The trial of five men accused of murdering former Bafana Bafana captain, Senzo Meyiwa continues in Pretori PRETORIA - The trial of five men accused of killing Senzo Meyiwa continues in the High Court in Pretoria. Forensic officer Thabo Mosia, who collected evidence from the crime scene, is on the witness stand. READ: Docuseries crew to stay in court as Meyiwa murder trial continues All of the men accused of the 2014 murder of the former Orlando Pirates goalkeeper have pleaded not guilty.